ffi::os_str::OsString::as_os_str.doc:
Converts to an [`OsStr`] slice.

# Examples

```
use std::ffi::{OsString, OsStr};

let os_string = OsString::from("foo");
let os_str = OsStr::new("foo");
assert_eq!(os_string.as_os_str(), os_str);
